data.description: Outstanding Value! DEEPLY Discounted Property in a Great Neighborhood!  This is where your search ends and the next exciting chapter of your life begins! Come and see this inviting and completely remodeled home.   Built-in 1990 but fully renovated in 2022, this house brings the rural setting of American life with all the finest conveniences today’s technology has to offer. With all new appliances, windows, fixtures, interior paint decor, and a fully completed addition of 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. The home used to be 1287 Sq. Ft. and it has been increased in size up to 1771 sq. ft. and is all permitted and done professionally. There is a Motorhome electrical hookup on the side of the home, a brand new 2-car carport, a brand-new sewer connection to city lines, and almost 1 acre of land to park all of your off-road vehicles. The home now boasts of 3 full bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. You are close to Palm Springs, fine dining and close to shopping, and schools.
